## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to implement a streaming, memory-bounded CSV processor with simple type validation and per-batch aggregation. It mirrors real-world data pipelines where inputs arrive line-by-line and must be validated before aggregation, without pulling the entire dataset into memory.

## Key Concepts

- Streaming iteration and batch processing
